1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,000
{\an8}<b><font color="#9CD5FF">One Pace Premium</font></b>
Keep the project alive: <font color="#a8c7fa">ko-fi.com/not6ip</font>

2
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:45,160
All right! Let's go, guys!

3
00:01:48,740 --> 00:01:50,380
What's the matter, Bepo?

4
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:57,180
Bepo, you didn't...

5
00:02:01,630 --> 00:02:02,810
Room!

6
00:02:11,170 --> 00:02:12,280
Scan!

7
00:02:15,850 --> 00:02:18,130
I knew it.

8
00:02:18,130 --> 00:02:22,370
Sorry.... I couldn't help myself, and...

9
00:02:23,030 --> 00:02:26,500
A-Am I gonna die, Captain?

10
00:02:26,500 --> 00:02:29,620
No way! You've just got the runs.

11
00:02:30,210 --> 00:02:33,120
Didn't I tell you not to eat fish from the river?

12
00:02:33,750 --> 00:02:35,840
Boy, the timing couldn't be any worse!

13
00:02:35,840 --> 00:02:38,800
I-I'm sorry...

14
00:02:46,890 --> 00:02:48,640
Stop acting cute!

15
00:02:50,350 --> 00:02:54,070
Man! Why's everyone causing trouble?

16
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:56,800
I hope they're laying low...

17
00:02:57,610 --> 00:02:58,760
Those morons...

18
00:03:00,740 --> 00:03:02,570
They're rebels!

19
00:03:05,170 --> 00:03:08,290
Boss! We have a group of lowlife rebels here!

20
00:03:08,290 --> 00:03:11,540
The magistrate killer, Zorojuro, is with them!

21
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:14,120
Fear not.

22
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:15,500
I'm on my way.

23
00:03:16,580 --> 00:03:19,510
One of them has a straw hat
around his neck, right?

24
00:03:19,510 --> 00:03:21,220
Y-Yes, sir!

25
00:03:21,220 --> 00:03:23,890
Do not engage.

26
00:03:24,640 --> 00:03:27,140
You are no match for them!

27
00:03:29,660 --> 00:03:31,520
How could you do that to the yokozuna?!

28
00:03:31,520 --> 00:03:33,520
You're just a damn nobody!

29
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:35,480
We'll teach you a lesson!

30
00:03:39,270 --> 00:03:42,860
Is Tama the brat who
Boss Holdem has captive?!

31
00:03:44,450 --> 00:03:47,240
You want her back?! Bring it on!

32
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:50,450
First a sumo match and now a sword fight?!

33
00:03:53,250 --> 00:03:54,830
Get them!

34
00:03:57,380 --> 00:04:00,670
Give us back Tama!

35
00:04:01,870 --> 00:04:03,800
He threw it again...

36
00:04:22,660 --> 00:04:24,410
Tama!

37
00:04:35,080 --> 00:04:37,120
What should I do?!

38
00:04:37,780 --> 00:04:39,210
You can stop acting.

39
00:04:40,050 --> 00:04:41,550
I'm not gonna help you!

40
00:04:42,760 --> 00:04:46,090
So I should also... c-cut them?

41
00:04:48,010 --> 00:04:49,350
Cut them!

42
00:04:49,930 --> 00:04:52,600
It's how you'll save the kid!

43
00:05:01,090 --> 00:05:02,190
Otama...

44
00:05:08,760 --> 00:05:10,030
I want to save her!

45
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:27,930
Give us back Tama!

46
00:05:32,850 --> 00:05:35,450
If you don't bring her here soon...

47
00:05:37,900 --> 00:05:40,060
we'll kill you all!

48
00:05:45,880 --> 00:05:48,110
Get out of my way!

49
00:06:17,260 --> 00:06:19,680
There's a commotion in the other town...

50
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:23,800
I'm hungry!

51
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:26,310
Stop it! You're acting dishonorably!

52
00:06:28,530 --> 00:06:33,130
A man of Wano must not whine!

53
00:06:33,130 --> 00:06:36,120
I'm hungry!

54
00:06:44,010 --> 00:06:45,460
Don't cry, don't cry.

55
00:06:46,580 --> 00:06:48,590
Miss Otsuru!

56
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:52,190
Miss Otsuru, do you have
any more five finger grass?

57
00:06:52,190 --> 00:06:52,860
What?

58
00:06:52,860 --> 00:06:57,720
My child was hungry and ended up
drinking the river water!

59
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:58,810
Oh my!

60
00:06:58,810 --> 00:07:00,440
Come inside! Quickly!

61
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:52,660
It's time to collect!

62
00:07:55,030 --> 00:07:57,910
Put your harvest on the pallet!

63
00:08:16,450 --> 00:08:18,060
S-Sir...

64
00:08:18,060 --> 00:08:20,430
Oh, your payment?

65
00:08:21,670 --> 00:08:23,140
F-Five silver...?!

66
00:08:23,140 --> 00:08:27,360
When you're done, slink out
the rear entrance, back home to Okobore!

67
00:08:27,360 --> 00:08:32,710
Please! This isn't enough
to feed my family for a week!

68
00:08:32,710 --> 00:08:35,030
We can't even buy water!

69
00:08:35,030 --> 00:08:37,160
Shut up! Don't complain!

70
00:09:09,610 --> 00:09:11,800
What's the name of your boss?!

71
00:09:11,800 --> 00:09:15,450
Bol... de... H-Holde...

72
00:09:15,450 --> 00:09:18,950
Hol... de... m...

73
00:09:21,780 --> 00:09:23,000
"Ball-de-boo"?

74
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:25,120
Get the firefighters!

75
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:29,170
Fire! A fire's started!

76
00:09:35,630 --> 00:09:40,010
Show yourself... Ball-de-boo!

77
00:09:40,570 --> 00:09:45,310
I won't forgive you if you've hurt Tama!

78
00:09:45,310 --> 00:09:47,440
Don't keep us waiting!

79
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:51,400
Ball-de-boo! Give us back Tama!

80
00:10:07,540 --> 00:10:11,630
Ball-de-boo!

81
00:10:17,260 --> 00:10:21,100
I'm right here, boy!

82
00:10:23,640 --> 00:10:26,480
So you're this town's boss...

83
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:29,190
Ball-de-boo! Right?!

84
00:10:30,100 --> 00:10:34,070
My name is Holdem!

85
00:10:41,450 --> 00:10:43,580
Boss Holdem!

86
00:10:43,580 --> 00:10:45,930
Kick his ass!

87
00:10:48,210 --> 00:10:49,540
Took you long enough!

88
00:10:50,530 --> 00:10:53,460
It's not like I had a choice!

89
00:10:53,460 --> 00:10:58,270
You sumo wrestled my house to the ground!

90
00:10:58,270 --> 00:11:03,260
Urashima crashed into it,
and now the building's in ruins!

91
00:11:03,260 --> 00:11:05,560
Who are you nobodies?!

92
00:11:18,610 --> 00:11:20,530
Big Bro!

93
00:11:20,530 --> 00:11:21,910
Tama!

94
00:11:21,910 --> 00:11:23,290
Otama!

95
00:11:30,660 --> 00:11:33,790
If you're bold enough to stand up against us...

96
00:11:34,450 --> 00:11:38,260
you must be underlings
of that thief, Shutenmaru!

97
00:11:39,930 --> 00:11:44,390
You shouldn't have messed with Bakura Town!

98
00:11:46,300 --> 00:11:49,270
Shutenmaru? What are you talking about?

99
00:11:52,650 --> 00:11:54,310
Shutenmaru...

100
00:11:54,310 --> 00:11:55,770
You punks...!

101
00:11:55,770 --> 00:11:59,110
It seems like you want this brat back...

102
00:11:59,110 --> 00:12:01,570
But don't you dare move!

103
00:12:01,570 --> 00:12:06,410
He can chew her up at any moment!

104
00:12:15,760 --> 00:12:17,920
Big Bro...!

105
00:12:19,850 --> 00:12:20,670
Tama...

106
00:12:36,250 --> 00:12:39,650
His gut is a lion?

107
00:12:39,650 --> 00:12:44,150
Boss Holdem is talking to
the straw-hat guy now!

108
00:12:45,320 --> 00:12:48,530
They'll throw down any minute now!

109
00:12:48,530 --> 00:12:51,620
Boss! What are your orders?!

110
00:12:52,730 --> 00:12:53,580
I'll be there soon!

111
00:12:54,530 --> 00:12:56,500
I'm in front of Bakura Town!

112
00:12:59,550 --> 00:13:02,380
Captain... Hawkins is at the entrance!

113
00:13:02,380 --> 00:13:04,720
And there's a fire in town.

114
00:13:04,720 --> 00:13:07,340
The cause of the fire is...

115
00:13:10,220 --> 00:13:13,230
Captain, don't abandon me...

116
00:13:14,370 --> 00:13:15,730
Don't tell me it's him.

117
00:13:15,730 --> 00:13:19,260
Yeah... I see Straw Hat...

118
00:13:19,260 --> 00:13:20,370
Huh?!

119
00:13:24,620 --> 00:13:26,570
Big Bro!

120
00:13:27,150 --> 00:13:29,530
I'll save you now, Tama!

121
00:13:29,530 --> 00:13:32,240
I have no intention of giving her back!

122
00:13:32,240 --> 00:13:34,710
You damn fool!

123
00:13:38,170 --> 00:13:39,630
Those idiots...!

124
00:13:53,890 --> 00:13:55,310
Open the gate!

125
00:13:57,030 --> 00:13:59,320
Open the gate!

126
00:14:10,390 --> 00:14:15,620
As usual, today's haul is chock-full
of delicious-looking food!

127
00:14:20,560 --> 00:14:24,240
That's right, Madam Speed.
Why don't you inspect it closely?

128
00:14:24,240 --> 00:14:25,840
The food is behind you!

129
00:14:25,840 --> 00:14:27,500
I can see it!

130
00:14:27,500 --> 00:14:28,150
What?

131
00:14:29,210 --> 00:14:30,880
I'll have you know...

132
00:14:30,880 --> 00:14:33,100
my field of vision...

133
00:14:33,100 --> 00:14:34,900
covers 350 degrees!

134
00:14:34,900 --> 00:14:36,300
You're like a horse!

135
00:14:36,300 --> 00:14:37,760
You think so?

136
00:14:39,310 --> 00:14:41,380
You smile like a horse, too!

137
00:14:50,990 --> 00:14:52,120
The fire bell?

138
00:14:52,120 --> 00:14:54,280
Fire! Fire!

139
00:14:54,280 --> 00:14:55,680
Clear the way!

140
00:14:55,680 --> 00:14:57,250
Move! Move!

141
00:14:58,230 --> 00:15:02,460
As the top firefighters belonging to
squad one, we hereby claim this fire!

142
00:15:07,380 --> 00:15:08,380
This place...

143
00:15:19,440 --> 00:15:21,430
Put out the fire!

144
00:15:23,420 --> 00:15:26,070
This is where Holdem lives...

145
00:15:28,020 --> 00:15:31,110
What could've destroyed it like this?!

146
00:15:31,110 --> 00:15:33,650
It's behind you, Madam Speed!

147
00:15:36,180 --> 00:15:37,800
I can see it.

148
00:15:37,800 --> 00:15:40,580
My field of vision is that of a horse, after all.

149
00:15:40,580 --> 00:15:43,960
I thought there was meant
to be a sumo event today...

150
00:15:45,100 --> 00:15:46,460
What's going on?

151
00:15:56,850 --> 00:15:59,460
Big Bro!

152
00:15:59,460 --> 00:16:02,270
Tama! I'll save you right now!

153
00:16:04,150 --> 00:16:05,710
Save her?!

154
00:16:05,710 --> 00:16:10,490
How are you gonna you save her?! Hmm?!

155
00:16:13,490 --> 00:16:15,090
Don't move!

156
00:16:15,090 --> 00:16:20,500
If you resist, then Kamijiro, the lion in my stomach...

157
00:16:23,870 --> 00:16:28,290
will chew up this brat's body.

158
00:16:35,930 --> 00:16:38,600
Otama! We'll save you!

159
00:16:39,110 --> 00:16:43,880
I'm gonna kick your ass if you don't
let go of Tama, Ball-de-boo!

160
00:16:43,880 --> 00:16:48,320
I told you my name is Holdem!
Get it right already!

161
00:16:52,740 --> 00:16:54,690
Big Bro!

162
00:16:55,200 --> 00:16:57,460
Okiku!

163
00:16:57,460 --> 00:16:59,370
Komachiyo!

164
00:17:02,110 --> 00:17:05,000
Spout off all you want, moron!

165
00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:07,750
I'm not gonna give her back to you!

166
00:17:07,750 --> 00:17:12,130
Why do you even want this
stupid brat back so much?!

167
00:17:12,130 --> 00:17:17,690
I suppose you must know about her ability!

168
00:17:38,450 --> 00:17:40,700
Now I can hold you guys hostage...

169
00:17:40,700 --> 00:17:44,160
and catch Shutenmaru, too!

170
00:17:45,500 --> 00:17:46,250
Who's that?

171
00:17:52,620 --> 00:17:54,630
Shutenmaru...

172
00:17:54,630 --> 00:17:58,010
Don't play dumb!

173
00:17:58,010 --> 00:18:01,390
He's the head of your thieves brigade!

174
00:18:03,640 --> 00:18:07,760
The recent robberies at the farm...

175
00:18:08,430 --> 00:18:11,890
are the work of the Mount Atama
Thieves, aren't they?!

176
00:18:12,550 --> 00:18:16,360
It may have been sheer dumb luck,
but you took down Urashima!

177
00:18:16,360 --> 00:18:19,820
So I bet you're one of his lieutenants!

178
00:18:21,870 --> 00:18:23,760
What are you talking about?

179
00:18:23,760 --> 00:18:25,090
Luffytaro...

180
00:18:26,420 --> 00:18:29,750
please do not anger him.

181
00:18:29,750 --> 00:18:32,500
He's already pretty angry!

182
00:18:38,260 --> 00:18:42,220
That's why you shouldn't
provoke him anymore!

183
00:18:43,590 --> 00:18:46,390
He may be strong, but...

184
00:18:48,780 --> 00:18:54,270
Holdem is not the real reason
the townsfolk are so terrified.

185
00:18:54,720 --> 00:18:56,740
They fear the man that has his back.

186
00:18:58,320 --> 00:18:59,860
The Beast Pirates...

187
00:19:00,990 --> 00:19:02,570
One of Kaido's top men...

188
00:19:06,530 --> 00:19:08,710
Jack the Drought...

189
00:19:08,710 --> 00:19:11,380
the true boss of Kuri!

190
00:19:14,460 --> 00:19:18,840
Isn't he the one who destroyed Zou?

191
00:19:18,840 --> 00:19:21,500
What? Oh, that guy!

192
00:19:22,600 --> 00:19:25,680
He used poison against that cat and dog...

193
00:19:29,890 --> 00:19:33,460
In the end, the elephant sent him flying, right?

194
00:19:48,570 --> 00:19:51,790
Jack went down with his ship!

195
00:19:51,790 --> 00:19:54,310
Didn't he die?

196
00:19:59,720 --> 00:20:02,880
Cat? Dog? Elephant?

197
00:20:03,700 --> 00:20:05,600
Are you talking about animals?

198
00:20:06,830 --> 00:20:09,600
So you are aware of Jack's accident at sea!

199
00:20:11,610 --> 00:20:13,730
Well, he's definitely not dead!

200
00:20:14,630 --> 00:20:18,730
He showed up here in
Bakura Town several days ago.

201
00:20:19,700 --> 00:20:20,990
What?!

202
00:20:21,810 --> 00:20:25,840
If you seriously anger Holdem now...

203
00:20:25,840 --> 00:20:29,160
Jack, one of the Calamities,
will come for revenge.

204
00:20:30,140 --> 00:20:33,560
If so, this town will become ruins.

205
00:20:34,090 --> 00:20:37,230
We can't let that happen!

206
00:20:37,230 --> 00:20:39,050
That's playing dirty!

207
00:20:39,050 --> 00:20:42,630
It's like they're holding
the whole town hostage!

208
00:20:49,770 --> 00:20:51,390
Hey!

209
00:20:51,390 --> 00:20:53,950
Hey, hey, hey, hey, hey, hey, hey!

210
00:20:53,950 --> 00:20:57,270
What are you guys talking about down there?!

211
00:20:59,570 --> 00:21:01,500
What's wrong?

212
00:21:01,500 --> 00:21:06,360
Why don't you try to
take back this little brat?!

213
00:21:06,360 --> 00:21:09,990
But if you move even by a hair's breadth...

214
00:21:12,950 --> 00:21:15,500
This is what will happen!

215
00:21:18,700 --> 00:21:21,760
It hurts!

216
00:21:23,090 --> 00:21:26,670
Stop it! You bastard!

217
00:21:31,850 --> 00:21:39,060
Ah, the sweet, anguished cries of the lowborn!

218
00:21:42,550 --> 00:21:45,570
Don't forget you're the one
who tossed that yokozuna...

219
00:21:45,570 --> 00:21:48,780
and destroyed my house!

220
00:22:05,110 --> 00:22:08,300
What's going on, Holdem?!

221
00:22:10,110 --> 00:22:15,340
It's Madam Speed's treasure ship
of provisions! Today's grub is here!

222
00:22:22,520 --> 00:22:25,460
That's a lot of food!

223
00:22:25,460 --> 00:22:27,780
That food's from Halcyon Farm...

224
00:22:29,850 --> 00:22:33,910
Clean water was used to grow it,
meaning it's free of toxins.

225
00:22:34,660 --> 00:22:37,230
Why do they get to keep it all?!

226
00:22:38,710 --> 00:22:41,000
Zoro! Could you handle that?!

227
00:22:41,940 --> 00:22:42,970
Okay...

228
00:22:42,970 --> 00:22:43,500
What?

229
00:22:44,280 --> 00:22:45,800
I'll save Tama!

230
00:22:45,800 --> 00:22:47,570
What? What?!

231
00:22:49,570 --> 00:22:54,450
Kiku! I'm sorry, but we've decided
to steal that and run.

232
00:22:54,450 --> 00:22:56,310
What? When?

233
00:22:58,900 --> 00:23:04,480
I'm sure it'll piss him off, but it won't be
as bad as just kicking his ass, right?

234
00:23:12,700 --> 00:23:14,490
Sir Hawkins!

235
00:23:16,240 --> 00:23:18,750
They're out of our league!

236
00:23:19,670 --> 00:23:21,320
Where's Holdem?

237
00:23:21,320 --> 00:23:23,790
He's in a mess at the fourth district's plaza!

238
00:23:26,900 --> 00:23:28,920
Holdem's not picking up.

239
00:23:35,850 --> 00:23:39,600
Stop right there, Basil Hawkins!

240
00:23:49,030 --> 00:23:50,110
Who are you?

241
00:23:51,150 --> 00:23:52,030
He's strong...

242
00:23:53,240 --> 00:23:57,330
Wano may be isolated from
news of the outside world...

243
00:23:57,330 --> 00:24:00,440
but he could identify us...

244
00:24:01,450 --> 00:24:03,000
I'd better make him disappear!

245
00:24:07,340 --> 00:24:08,780
And now...

246
00:24:10,080 --> 00:24:13,180
the real fun starts!

247
00:24:16,760 --> 00:24:20,100
I don't care if you happen to
kill one or two of them in the process!

248
00:24:20,100 --> 00:24:23,020
Hurry the hell up and grab them!

249
00:24:27,730 --> 00:24:29,530
Hey, woman!

250
00:24:29,530 --> 00:24:34,740
You remember that this brat
is our hostage, right?!

251
00:24:45,570 --> 00:24:48,290
Luffytaro... Zorojuro...

252
00:24:48,980 --> 00:24:49,820
Why...?

253
00:24:49,820 --> 00:24:51,670
Look what you've done!

254
00:24:51,670 --> 00:24:57,640
Oh, I see now! You don't
need the brat back, right?!

255
00:24:57,640 --> 00:25:01,610
Then, I'll have her chewed up as you wish!

256
00:25:01,610 --> 00:25:03,440
Go ahead, Kamijiro!

257
00:25:23,650 --> 00:25:24,410
What?!

258
00:25:24,410 --> 00:25:25,980
The brat's gone!

259
00:25:32,010 --> 00:25:34,590
Huh?! When did he get her?!

260
00:25:34,590 --> 00:25:37,930
Kamijiro! What the hell are you doing?!

261
00:26:04,700 --> 00:26:07,370
Let's get out of here, Tama!

262
00:26:08,190 --> 00:26:10,000
Big Bro...!

263
00:26:10,000 --> 00:26:12,380
Sorry to keep you waiting!

264
00:26:14,100 --> 00:26:15,890
Komachiyo!

265
00:26:18,010 --> 00:26:19,640
Kamijiro!

266
00:26:23,740 --> 00:26:27,140
I'll cut you to shreds with my flaming sword!

267
00:26:33,860 --> 00:26:40,240
No one's ever gotten away
from this trick sword!

268
00:26:41,070 --> 00:26:44,450
Hellfire Edge!

269
00:26:49,300 --> 00:26:52,880
I got you! Come on!
You're gonna be our hostage, too!

270
00:26:56,380 --> 00:26:59,590
You don't care if your friend dies?!

271
00:27:05,560 --> 00:27:08,130
Drop your swords now!

272
00:27:14,650 --> 00:27:16,610
Yeah, that's it!

273
00:27:16,610 --> 00:27:18,650
Zorojuro...

274
00:27:18,650 --> 00:27:23,640
You stay right there!
I'm gonna beat you to death!

275
00:27:31,590 --> 00:27:33,170
Hey...

276
00:27:33,170 --> 00:27:35,720
I still won't help you.

277
00:27:42,130 --> 00:27:45,110
Don't you care about her?!

278
00:27:50,520 --> 00:27:52,400
I won't let you get away!

279
00:27:58,010 --> 00:27:59,490
Pardon me.

280
00:28:02,690 --> 00:28:03,740
What should I do?

281
00:28:03,740 --> 00:28:05,450
Take care of your side!

282
00:28:05,450 --> 00:28:06,550
Okay!

283
00:28:49,400 --> 00:28:51,410
Dog! This way!

284
00:28:58,880 --> 00:29:01,010
Thank you!

285
00:29:09,970 --> 00:29:11,520
Get us out of town!

286
00:29:25,660 --> 00:29:27,940
What happened to your cheek?

287
00:29:31,570 --> 00:29:33,000
It's nothing.

288
00:29:34,210 --> 00:29:36,920
It was just pulled by some pincers.

289
00:29:37,790 --> 00:29:39,330
My millet dumplings...

290
00:29:40,120 --> 00:29:42,800
can't even come out like that though!

291
00:29:44,930 --> 00:29:46,010
Pincers?!

292
00:29:47,680 --> 00:29:49,720
Give me a minute!

293
00:29:50,700 --> 00:29:52,470
Stop running!

294
00:29:57,690 --> 00:30:03,610
Big Bro! I'm fine now!
You already saved me!

295
00:30:05,490 --> 00:30:07,870
Hm?! You want some?!

296
00:30:08,200 --> 00:30:11,080
Roar! Lion Fire!

297
00:30:18,170 --> 00:30:20,790
Big Bro!

298
00:30:20,790 --> 00:30:27,380
Witness the next level of my trick sword!

299
00:30:30,010 --> 00:30:32,430
Gum-Gum...

300
00:30:35,770 --> 00:30:38,350
Red Hawk!

